Package cams.dashboards.menu

Class OrganiserUI

java.lang.Object
cams.dashboards.menu.OrganiserUI
All Implemented Interfaces:
DashboardState
public class OrganiserUI
extends java.lang.Object
implements DashboardState
Class containing methods for various camp management functionalities in the dashboard. These methods include actions like assigning students to camps, changing camp details, and deleting camps.

    • assignStudent

      protected void assignStudent​(Dashboard dashboard, java.lang.String selectedCamp)
      UI interaction that assigns a student to a selected camp as a participationController. This method prompts for the userID of a student and assigns them to the specified camp.
      Parameters:
      dashboard - The dashboard context.
      selectedCamp - The name of the camp to assign the student to.

    • deleteCamp

      protected void deleteCamp​(Dashboard dashboard, java.lang.String selectedCamp)
      Responsible for user interaction in the process of deleting a camp.
